<p>From <a href="https://x.com/cshearer41">Catriona Agg&#8217;s endlessly rewarding Twitter feed</a>:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/2025-10-17-square-deal.jpg" alt="https://x.com/Cshearer41/status/1761786951424671868" width="391" height="388" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-71963" srcset="https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/2025-10-17-square-deal.jpg 391w, https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/2025-10-17-square-deal-300x298.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 391px) 100vw, 391px" /></p>
<p>The three smaller squares are the same size. What&#8217;s the angle? (The outermost shape too is a square.)</p>

